name: BMO Corporate Discount Bond ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to provide exposure to the performance of a portfolio of fixed income securities and generate income, primarily by investing in investment grade Canadian corporate fixed income securities that trade near or below par value. The fund will primarily invest in a variety of investment grade rated corporate fixed income securities that are issued in Canada with a remaining term to maturity between one and ten years. The selected fixed income securities will primarily trade near or below par value.
